{"tid":565120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郵輪海中心爆騷亂　警衛與滋事者困獸鬥","createTime":"2018-02-18T16:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T17:34:33.000Z","uid":53379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eed7690c1d0294e9d22993a9aa10e19929fcdc20","tid":565120,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">郵輪海中心爆騷亂　警衛與滋事者困獸鬥</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180218/s00005/9cd5f05ff0e3be2d71c25e76fd8ce7c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180218%2Fs00005%2F9cd5f05ff0e3be2d71c25e76fd8ce7c0.jpg&h=4c1923a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國嘉年華公司一艘郵輪在南太平洋中心爆發騷亂。船上警衛與滋事者對峙混戰，一些乘客為免受波及自鎖在房中。整艘郵輪猶如「無政府狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n涉事郵輪是「嘉年華傳奇」號，可容納逾2000人，日前由澳洲墨爾本航行至法國海外屬地新喀里多尼亞。<br />\n<br />\n目前船公司和警方均未公布事發原因，只知引起衝突一方是個「大家族」，共有23人上船。有乘客聲稱目擊一名乘客踩到「大家族」一位成員的拖鞋，結果對方大發脾氣；有人則稱他們自起航開始四處挑釁，例如在泳池吐口水、在吸煙區大吵大鬧、跟其他乘客或者船員毆鬥等。船員多次吩咐乘客鎖孩童在客艙內，成人亦不應單獨前往甲板。<br />\n<br />\n船上緊張局面持續數日，上周四（15日）晚更爆發大規模騷亂。數名滋事者與部分乘客起衝突，之後有愈來愈多人加入。警衛制止時不分派別，向所有在場人士施加武力拳打腳踢，還試圖搶走在旁拍攝者相機，情況混亂。<br />\n<br />\n經過大約45分鐘，警衛終於完全控制現場，鎖部分滋事者入房軟禁，待澳洲警方登船帶走，事件方告一段落。外國傳媒報道，他們下船時，郵輪上有多名乘客拍手叫好。<br />\n<br />\n嘉年華公司上周六（17日）發表聲明，稱遊輪已返回墨爾本，向受影響乘客致歉。聲明提到，網上流傳影片所見警衛行為不符合公司政策，會檢討和調查整件事原因；受影響乘客可獲優惠券，下次乘坐遊輪享七五折優惠。有乘客認為，如此道歉並不足夠，明言以後不會再光顧嘉年華公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P1c2s0dQD3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP1c2s0dQD3g&d=2bcU3BXsMNDy0vb8v51sIG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=affc44cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P1c2s0dQD3g</a><br />\n（華盛頓郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180218/s00005/1518963392546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180218%2Fs00005%2F1518963392546&d=2bcU3BXsMNDy0vb8v51sIG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f651da81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180218%2Fs00005%2F1518963392546&h=951501ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180218/s00005/1518963392546</a>"},{"pid":"4c3c891be22d945712db572839a6fc99cb9b12cd","tid":565120,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲以為係啓德郵輪碼頭到發生tim"},{"pid":"4de4457485c65396a537cae3682bebf5e7bc65f1","tid":565120,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"巴拿馬總統都同我有d交情"},{"pid":"7d88bae355f2992baf677b9fe12bf2bfad715124","tid":565120,"uid":168222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"美國唔意外啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d094bed10c93836f18875f739c89af64df11709f","tid":565120,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"可以拍成電影"},{"pid":"b8f48250a11e375f3feab52f07f90e1b9ada3a04","tid":565120,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"到咗公海未？"},{"pid":"0788a8978eaa317d91895b8e9d8e54cfddbbb182","tid":565120,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"又係垃圾支那蝗搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0123c614c3ee0cf5c0a3ab3779d6b6f018b8accd","tid":565120,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d88bae355f2992baf677b9fe12bf2bfad715124","tid":565120,"uid":168222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"美國唔意外啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"美國公司, 不過依條係澳洲航線黎啊Ching<br />\n主要客源係澳洲人<br />\n搞事個家族係意裔澳洲人, 一共廿三條友全部比人趕落船"},{"pid":"d70df0a163e45991455509a80baf8